In	Up	Ec	Ex	Rq	Gr	Re	In	Up	Ec	Ex	Rq	Gr	Re
InCR Instantiate a new Internal Audit Assessment
UpCR Update details relating to Internal Audit Assessment
EcCR Accept, verify, etc. aspects of Internal Audit Assessment processing
ExCR Execute an available automated action for Internal Audit Assessment
RqCR Request manual intervention or a decision with respect to Internal Audit Assessment
GrCR Obtain permission to act in relation to Internal Audit Assessment
ReCR Retrieve details about any aspect of Internal Audit Assessment
